    {
        "url": "/quotes/samantha_shannon_618171",
        "quote": "I was mostly an indoor girl at university. Where other students did drama or music or sport alongside their degrees, I wrote. I used to work on essays and classwork during the day and 'The Bone Season' in the evenings.",
