    {
        "url": "/quotes/samantha_shannon_618172",
        "quote": "J. K. Rowling is one of my favourite authors, and I really admire how she created this big wizarding world. But I think our books are very, very different, and I don't think there can be a next J. K. Rowling. She is one of a kind.",
