    {
        "url": "/quotes/samantha_shannon_618178",
        "quote": "My English teachers gave me a copy of Atwood's 'The Handmaid's Tale' when I left high school, which has always been very special to me - it was the novel that introduced me to dystopian fiction. I'm also influenced by Edgar Allan Poe, Dickens, John Wyndham and Middle English dream-visions.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Samantha Shannon",
            "url": "/quotes/samantha_shannon_618178"
