    {
        "url": "/quotes/samantha_shannon_618156",
        "quote": "I always felt that sci-fi and fantasy were my thing. Bit of a geek, I'm afraid. But I like creating worlds, and I felt it was a genre that gave me more freedom. It just seemed like I belonged there.",
