    {
        "url": "/quotes/samantha_shannon_618146",
        "quote": "I am the first one to go to university in my family. I am the first writer as well. My dad is a retired policeman, and my mom works for a glass-processing company. She is health-and-safety manager, and my stepfather is a plumber. I have four half siblings, one from my mom's marriage and three from my dad's marriage, so we are kind of scattered.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Samantha Shannon",
            "url": "/quotes/samantha_shannon_618146"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Half",
