                "name": "Works",
                "url": "/topics/works"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/samantha_shannon_618164",
        "quote": "I was a hacker of sorts. Not a mind 'reader,' exactly; more a mind 'radar,' in tune with the workings of the aether. I could sense the nuances of dreamscapes and rogue spirits. Things outside myself. Things the average voyant wouldn't feel.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Samantha Shannon",
            "url": "/quotes/samantha_shannon_618164"
